race.description: Express Smash Repairs Midway Conditional Handicap
race.comment: YOUR NOT THE BOSS (11) solid gelding who will find this more to his liking third-up. Looks to have a good win in him this campaign after closing late when seventh over 1200m at Moruya. Looking for this trip and further now and no excuses today. LETHAL LOVE (12) All Too Hard filly starting to hit her straps. Should handle the rise in class and trip after making it two straight wins when saluting in good time over 1200m at Bathurst. Key jockey change from the low draw. Hard to hold out. PRETTY SASSY (13) sprinted quickly with the 59kg when scoring first-up at Nowra. Covered ground from the sticky draw when a fading fifth over 1200m at this track at latest. No surprise to see her take a hand in the finish. C'MON MATE (4) just over a month between runs when a handy fifth over 1200m at Wagga. Kept fresh again with a host of gear changes. Stays in the calculations from the draw.
